      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint, showroom condition and stands as one of the finest examples available today. The exterior paint is flawless, boasting a deep, glass-like finish without a single chip, scratch, or swirl mark. Inside, the cabin remains in pristine state, smelling fresh and showing zero signs of wear on the premium upholstery. Mechanically, the car is perfect, having been meticulously stored in a climate-controlled environment and serviced strictly according to schedule. This is a collector-grade vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the factory.",
