    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and it\u2019s honestly been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has tons of life left for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so it runs smoothly and still looks great parked in the driveway. It's the perfect reliable daily driver for someone who wants a quality car without the brand-new price tag. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.7,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is a driver-focused E46 M3 featuring the high-revving S54 3.2L inline-six engine equipped with individual throttle bodies for exceptional throttle response. This example utilizes the sought-after Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox, delivering power to the rear wheels through a variable M-differential lock. The chassis has been maintained with technical foresight, including a documented VANOS system overhaul and proactive subframe reinforcement to ensure structural rigidity under lateral load. Suspension components remain tight, utilizing a MacPherson strut front and multi-link rear setup that preserves the car's legendary 50/50 weight distribution. While the exterior and interior show honest signs of use, the powertrain exhibits excellent compression and smooth power delivery across the entire 8,000 RPM range.",
      "price": 33500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_8_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_8",
      "description": "Used car. Good condition. Runs well. Clean interior. Maintenance records available.",
      "price": 29500.0,
      "reputation": 0.4,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 25
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Presented in a striking metallic finish, this vehicle has been a reliable and cherished daily driver. The exterior retains a high-gloss shine, though closer inspection reveals a few minor surface scratches and small stone chips on the hood, typical of careful road use. Step inside to find a cabin that has been kept smoke-free and clean; the leather upholstery is in great shape with only light creasing on the driver\u2019s bolster. All power features, including the sunroof, heated seats, and navigation system, are fully operational. Under the hood, the engine runs smoothly and the transmission shifts effortlessly, backed by a consistent maintenance log and a recent oil change. With a set of high-quality tires showing deep tread and a firm, responsive braking system, this car is mechanically sound and ready for the open road. It offers a premium driving experience without the new-car price tag.",
      "price": 34800.0,
